# Frontend React

## API

- Endpoints only in `src/apiConfig.js` — never hardcode `/api/...`
- Dev proxy: `package.json` → `"proxy": "http://localhost:5000"`

## Key routes

| Route | Page |
|-------|------|
| `/` | PortfolioPage |
| `/:ticker` | SummaryPage |
| `/:ticker/financials` | FinancialsPage |
| `/screener` | StockScreenerPage |
| `/admin` | AdminConsolePage |
| `/ticker/:ticker` | TickerDetailsPage (insiders) |

## Free-first UX

- Empty states should say "Run bootstrap from Admin" when cache is empty.
- Show `meta.source` when present (`sqlite`, `sec_edgar`, `nasdaq`, `disabled`).
- Bootstrap/Reactstrap + ApexCharts; Redux only for screener state.

## Tests

- Run: `npm test -- --watchAll=false`
